"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Moscow and China have been talking about building a pipeline for a long time, but they haven't started building it yet. Moscow says they have now reached an understanding on the project.\",            \"english_title\": \"Pipeline Talks\",            \"translated_version\": \"Mosc\u00fa y China han estado hablando sobre construir un tubo por mucho tiempo, pero a\u00fan no han empezado a construirlo. Mosc\u00fa dice que ahora tienen un acuerdo sobre el proyecto.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Conversaciones sobre el tubo\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The World Health Organization has reported that there are now 139 suspected deaths and 600 cases in their latest update.\",            \"english_title\": \"WHO Update\",            \"translated_version\": \"La Organizaci\u00f3n Mundial de la Salud ha informado que ahora hay 139 muertes sospechosas y 600 casos en su \u00faltima actualizaci\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Actualizaci\u00f3n de la OMS\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Jeff Landry visited Greenland, which is a semi-autonomous part of Denmark. His visit has upset some people in Greenland.\",            \"english_title\": \"Visit to Greenland\",            \"translated_version\": \"Jeff Landry visit\u00f3 Groenlandia, que es una parte semi-aut\u00f3noma de Dinamarca. Su visita molest\u00f3 a algunas personas en Groenlandia.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Visita a Groenlandia\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Sana Yousaf's murder in Pakistan shows a pattern of violence against women, according to activists.\",            \"english_title\": \"Violence Against Women\",            \"translated_version\": \"El asesinato de Sana Yousaf en Pakist\u00e1n muestra un patr\u00f3n de violencia contra las mujeres, seg\u00fan activistas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Violencia contra mujeres\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A former power minister was sentenced to 75 years in jail in absentia earlier this month.\",            \"english_title\": \"Minister Sentenced\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un exministro de energ\u00eda fue sentenciado a 75 a\u00f1os de c\u00e1rcel en ausencia a principios de este mes.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ministro sentenciado\"        }    ]}"